name: Thank You Lord
description: Brand New CD in 2012 from Reggie & Ladye Love!  Songs include:  Above All, No One Ever Cared, I Will Serve Thee, He Washed My Eyes With Tears, He Looked Beyond, Thank You Lord, Burdens Are Lifted at Calvary, You Raise Me Up, I Have Fixed My Mind, Whatever It Takes, Softly and Tenderly, The Solid Rock, In The Heart of Jesus.

name: Miracle
description:
Reggie & Ladye's latest project, 'The Miracle," produced by legendary producer Lari Goss features 12 inspirational songs by some of gospel music's top songwriters.
Song list: 1) I Have Decided 2) Hold On 3) Can He Could He Would He 4) I Will Still Trust In You 5) John The Baptist 6) The Miracle 7) God Gave The Song 8) I'm Not There Yet 9) I've Got A Song 10) He Knows The Way Home 11) I've Got Good News 12) Somewhere Between Heaven and Earth

name: Standards
description:
"This project is very special to us. My dad was in World War II & played in the big band aboard ship. He later played in his collegiate band & subsequently I (Ladye) grew up singing big band music. He is featured on 'Moonglow' and it was a joy to do this project with him."

Songs include:
1) It Had To Be You
2) Let's Fall In Love
3) I Left My Heart In San Francisco
4) That's All
5) Moonglow
6) Medley (Embraceable You, Don't Get Around Much Anymore, All of Me)
7) The Way You Look Tonight
8) They Can't Take That Away From Me
9) Besame Mucho
10) The Very Thought of You
11) I'll Be Seeing You
